{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act26side", "eventName": "空想花庭", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "HE-7", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "以愛相連", "storyInfo": "夜幕消退，晨光熹微，主教業已做好準備。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g7_chapel", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sweep"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_open_door", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主教閣下，您來了。", "name": "瘦削的修道院居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天輪到你打掃禮拜堂啊，約里。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "辛苦了。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該的。最近發生了很多事，本來也睡得不安穩。", "name": "約里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來幫您拿聖餐吧。", "name": "約里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，不用了......", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊對，瞧我，手上全是灰塵。", "name": "約里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，您有沒有聞到什麼味道......隱隱約約的......", "name": "約里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇怪的味道嗎？", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，很好聞，很清新，我能從中感受到一種......生命力。", "name": "約里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "具體的，我說不上來，像是站在下風口，雖然分辨不出源頭，但循著這個味道，往前走......往前走肯定能到一個什麼地方。", "name": "約里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#7$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該是花香，約里。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小麥粉不夠了，今天聖餐裡無酵餅的原料，有三分之一是可食用花粉。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地窖裡還剩下的那幾瓶葡萄酒有些酸了，所以我也撒了些花粉在裡面。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前兩年花期還沒有結束的時候，克萊芒就提前收割了一些花朵，曬乾，製成粉末，存在地窖裡......", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他愛護那些美麗的花朵，他也愛護我們。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......", "name": "約里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是修道院離開這裡前的最後一次聖餐，但我們的存糧已經見底，只好把每個人的聖餐份額減半，還要摻些......雜糧。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#5$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，您別這樣說。況且今天的聖餐，讓人有胃口極了......", "name": "約里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此，約里，你趕快回房間洗把臉，晨會之前和其他人一起過來。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剩下的準備工作，我自己來就好。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "約里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主教閣下，今天之後，我們都會被拯救嗎？", "name": "約里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人，薩科塔、薩卡茲......這座修道院裡的所有人，都會被拯救嗎？", "name": "約里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是明明杰拉爾德已經......", "name": "約里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你先去吧，約里。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那，待會見，主教閣下。", "name": "約里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_939_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老人掩上了門。"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他緩慢地走到了禱告台上。"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年邁的安布羅修修道院主教，斯特凡諾·托雷格羅薩，開始將聖餐中的無酵餅和葡萄酒小心地分成一份一份。"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他低著頭，時候尚早，還很曖昧的晨光從聖像後的窗戶透進來，聖像的表情隱沒在黑暗裡。他的表情也同樣看不分明。"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會的。我們都會得到拯救。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g3_abandonsancturay_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她走進傾頹的聖堂，一些徒留形狀的植物根莖在她的腳下化作齏粉。"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屋頂的拱形承重結構已經在大火中倒塌，聖堂暴露在天光之下。"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風早已吹散刺鼻的焦味，但滿眼都是斷壁殘垣，短時間內沒有人會來整理。"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除非重建，那場大火的痕跡永遠不會消失。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她看了一眼躺倒在地板上的半截聖像，突然扭過頭去，看向身後空蕩蕩的地方。"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cellodoubt"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們總是掙扎，翻來覆去地自我拷問、自我開解，就像奏鳴曲來到高潮段落，弦鍵紛飛，快慢錯落，激昂，縈回。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下定決心後的那刻，奏鳴曲則進入平緩悠長的尾聲，這是一種脫力後的虛無，但又無比決絕。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "情感是複雜的，但情感的變化總是相似，旋律工整得讓人沒有驚喜。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我感受到了你的平靜，所以你終於做好了選擇。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管怎樣，我應該演奏你。最後的時刻，你應該聽見自己的心聲。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "迷途的、豐沛的靈魂啊。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g12_anbandonspace", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些罈子，還有案板......烘焙的痕跡，但空氣中並沒有殘留發酵的味道......嗯，無酵餅確實也不需要發酵。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來這裡就是準備聖餐的場地了。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "某種異物的碎屑，暫時分辨不出來歷......摸起來很潮濕，是因為在地下嗎......", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桌角還殘留著一些小麥粉......為什麼也會這麼黏稠......", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個味道......", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那位虔誠的主教，努力到最後，只能選擇這樣一條路嗎？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科那邊還是聯繫不上......直接把這些資訊告訴奧倫？那事情會變得更加麻煩。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，不會真的要我來處理吧？伊比利亞那邊的東西，我瞭解得可不多啊。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#10$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，頭疼。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g8_outsidepath", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特勤部隊很快便會全部到達修道院外圍......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到時候我出去指揮他們布防，封鎖出入路徑，你留在裡面接應，配合我們突入。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧倫，你確定要這麼做嗎？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯普莉雅，你見完蕾繆安後，就倒向她那邊了嗎？我不覺得有浪費時間再解釋這個的必要。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我會直接攔住你，奧倫。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "學姐？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_electrcwhlchrrll", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，還是被追上了。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯普莉雅，攔住她，我出去接應。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我拒絕。你沒看見學姐的表情那麼嚴肅嗎？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她兇起來很可怕的，當年把我從學校的小房間裡揪出來，沒收了我剛發明的無人機，到現在都還沒還給我。我可不願意和她唱反調。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯普莉雅，謝謝。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧倫，你的心思一直都不在如何說服主教將這座修道院帶回拉特蘭上。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是你的工作。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一開始的計劃，便是不放任何一個薩卡茲離開這裡，為此甚至私下調動了特勤部隊......", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "五個十人隊......是我能力的極限。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#8$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧倫，你視拉特蘭的律法為何物？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回到拉特蘭後，我會領受教宗閣下的責罰......雖然我不覺得自己所做的事情應該被懲處。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該清楚，這樣一支拉特蘭軍隊突入修道院，會造成什麼後果。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是薩科塔，還是薩卡茲，裡面那些離群的人，就像一群在荒野上迷路的旅人，這座殘破的修道院是他們最後取暖的篝火。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "篝火會指引前來救援的衣衫整潔的同胞，篝火也會吸引同樣流浪到此的其他落魄的旅人。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們無依無靠，他們脆弱驚惶，他們依然保持著可貴的善良。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以杰拉爾德才會以死來懇求我們......也以死來命令他帶領的那些薩卡茲，讓雙方維持和平。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#5$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如果篝火招來的是野獸呢？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#5$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我真想能像你一樣，說點漂亮話，做些討人喜歡的工作，蕾繆安樞機輔佐官。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是沒辦法，你沒有跟著成千上萬的流民穿過戰亂後的荒野，在倫蒂尼姆城外看見那片遮天蔽日的烏雲。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過講真的，我原本以為至少你能和我有點默契，至少能考慮到，把那群薩卡茲放走會有多大的隱患吧？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲在維多利亞的暴行有目共睹，他們散播的恐懼在這片大地上不斷蔓延。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你真的相信教宗閣下的計劃，覺得萬國信使有其價值，那更應該明白，拉特蘭為什麼不能對他們心慈手軟。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬國峰會之後，拉特蘭為各國搭建起的友好關係，比這走廊上糊的窗戶紙還脆弱。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修道院裡的薩卡茲心懷怨恨，又受到阿爾圖羅源石技藝的影響，他們一旦離開，很可能用盡各種手段報復。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "況且，拉特蘭的移動修道院竟然與薩卡茲勾結了這麼多年，如果這段經歷被傳播出去......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭又該如何在泰拉諸國間以其聖潔自居？又該如何維繫本就勉強建立的外交關係？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰火洗劫後的聖城將變成什麼樣子？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而五個十人隊，足以平息這座修道院裡的任何事端，將一切都扼殺在萌芽中。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#8$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但裡面的薩卡茲，只是一些獵人、農戶......唯一的雇傭兵，已經死在了我們的面前。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#8$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你所謂的平息事端，將會是一場屠殺。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在思慮未來該如何維護拉特蘭的聖潔之時，你便已經玷污了它，不覺得可笑嗎？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可笑的是你，蕾繆安。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#6$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "據我所知，“噤聲的蕾繆安”處理這類事情時可是連眼睛都不眨的。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#6$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是病床上那五年的沉睡改變了你的性格，還是......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#6$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個號稱“殉道者”的傢伙影響了你——", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#6$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punchsp5"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.8, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.3}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧倫沒能說出那個名字。"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "輪椅突進到面前，狙擊銃的銃管狠狠捅在他的腰間，他靠在牆壁上才沒有摔倒，咬牙讓自己吃痛的聲音不至於變調。"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶——", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你繼續說。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#10$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......“噤聲的蕾繆安”。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......說了學姐不好惹。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g4_gatheringplace_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_371_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$escape_intro", "key": "$escape_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_371_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第二分隊已經抵達目標地點，爆破物設置完畢。", "name": "年輕的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_371_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "依據安布羅修修道院的建築圖紙，他們已成功控制了三處可用的逃生通道。", "name": "年輕的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_371_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "內部人員如果強行向外突破，爆炸將直接導致通道坍塌，將他們堵回去......", "name": "年輕的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_371_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該會把人直接埋在下面吧，二隊那個傢伙之前笑嘻嘻地回覆我說，定點爆炸太麻煩了，而且沒什麼必要。", "name": "老練的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_371_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "年輕的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_371_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你繼續。", "name": "老練的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_371_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第三、第四分隊已完成分散部署，佔據制高點，確保修道院各個方位均在狙擊視野內。", "name": "年輕的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_371_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一切準備就緒。", "name": "年輕的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_371_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很好，部署時間與計劃一致。", "name": "老練的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報告奧倫閣下：我們隨時待命，準備清剿修道院內的薩卡茲。", "name": "老練的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "重複：我們已經就位。", "name": "老練的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "老練的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_371_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "年輕的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_371_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有回音。", "name": "老練的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_371_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......情勢嚴峻。", "name": "年輕的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_371_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，別擔心，他很可能只是在吃超大份可麗餅，騰不出手而已。", "name": "老練的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_371_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的情況......很多嗎？", "name": "年輕的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_371_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "稀鬆平常。這是你第一次執行特別任務吧，鎮靜啦，拉特蘭會護佑你。", "name": "老練的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，做好準備，如果始終無法聯繫到奧倫閣下，或者有任何異動，我們直接從正門突入。", "name": "老練的拉特蘭特勤隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g1_monasteryentrance", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "channel": "escape1", "volume": 0.5, "loop": "false", "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#4$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——走廊沒人。快，我們往這邊跑。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#4$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是往修道院外走的路？我們不是要一起去找杰拉爾德叔叔嗎？", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#4$2"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。我要先將你帶到安全的地方，福爾圖娜。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒聽到嗎？那幫拉特蘭人要強行接管這座修道院，軍隊可不會像那個叫斯普莉雅的女人一樣，用看管和安撫這樣“仁慈”的手段。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#11$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不能出現在拉特蘭軍隊面前，你剛剛墮天，在他們眼裡，你現在也是惡......", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#11$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說下去，萊蒙德，我願意聽。", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別......別像菲娜那樣被我打斷。", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，福爾圖娜，我只是想說，你在我心裡的樣子從來都沒有變過。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，你現在的處境和我們這些薩卡茲一樣，留下來也只會給修道院的其他人添麻煩......", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#11$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯。", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#1$2"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽你的。", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#1$2"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，萊蒙德，那你呢？你會不會有事？", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，杰拉爾德老大已經把事情都安排好了，就連剛剛我們聽到的那些事，憑他的本事，也應該預料到了。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#9$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等找到地方安頓好你，我再回來幫他。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#9$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#8$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊蒙德，你的手心出了很多汗，臉色也不太好，怎麼了？", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，從剛剛開始，老有種說不上來的感覺，好像有什麼東西壓著......", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#8$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能是跑得太快了，早上還沒有吃東西，有點心慌吧。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#8$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒這些事情，這個時間，我們應該在和杰拉爾德老大，還有大家一起領聖餐......", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#3$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#8$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以後還有很多機會。", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#8$2"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深呼吸，萊蒙德，現在換我帶著你跑。", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#8$2"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#8$2", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.5}